sequenceDiagram
  participant Caller
  participant Retell
  participant API
  participant DB
  Caller->>Retell: asks to move appointment
  Retell->>API: search_availability
  API->>DB: live slot lookup
  DB-->>API: alternatives
  Caller->>Retell: confirms new slot
  Retell->>API: reschedule_appointment
  API->>DB: transaction mark old RESCHEDULED + create new CONFIRMED
  DB-->>API: new appointment
  API-->>Retell: speak new slot and fee only if applicable
